	-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	About
	-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Introduction:

	<<Pandora2>> conforms a bundle of jpa-jsf utilities who works together in order to provide base ejb managers and base backing beans controller hierarchy.

What is and what is not:

	First, let's say that <<Pandora2>>:

		* Is not a seam extension.

		* Is not a cdi implementation.

		* Is just a couple of utilities and templates that can be used in any java project in order to generalize some common's patterns behaviors.

		* Take a quick view and you'll find out that p2 is only composed of 70+ java classes and there's not restriction at all for combine these components with any other java technology.

Download:

	<<Pandora2>> can be downloaded:

		* Directly as binary distribution jar file from {{{http://repository.pandora2.com.ar/maven2/com/ebizlink/pandora2/}here.}}

		* As maven2 dependency.

Configure maven dependency:

+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
<repository>
	<id>pandora2</id>
	<url>http://repository.pandora2.com.ar/maven2/</url>
</repository>
+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
<dependency>
	<groupId>com.ebizlink</groupId>
	<artifactId>pandora2</artifactId>
	<version>04.xx.xx</version>
</dependency>
+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

